_sText:
This map contains the original scoutzknivez map, with addition an arena above, and two teleports. This map was mainly made for RPG servers for 1on1 scout battles and such (e.g. noscoping) I'm sorry I do not know who made ScoutzKnivez. This map can also be played on deathmatch... a lot of fun.
ScoutzKnivez_Arena = SKA

=============================

As of June 2nd, 2008 little glitches and bugs have been fixed, and the new file is out named scoutzknivez_arena_fix
